{"tid":1979241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手足案件一週總結 (希望大家唔好唔記得佢哋)","createTime":"2020-04-19T09:38:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T03:31:08.000Z","uid":40542,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b67cf5d33deb9c7e3f585ce973f0fa9300e4b3b5","tid":1979241,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T09:38:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>一週總結 (截至2020年4月18日)</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n被告: 1141 -&gt; 1170<br />\n已結束: 70 -&gt; 77<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">被判入獄: 7 -&gt; 9</span></ins></strong> (其中1位獲准保釋等候上訴)<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">被判入勞教中心/更生中心: 3 -&gt; 5<br />\n還押/拘留: 88</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n暴動: 544 -&gt; 546<br />\n管有攻擊性/違禁武器: 167<br />\n企圖襲警/襲警: 106 -&gt; 107<br />\n縱火相關控罪: 46<br />\n爆炸相關控罪: 18<br />\n槍械相關控罪: 9<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>還押個案</ins></strong><br />\n1. <strong><ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">林(21)</span></ins></strong> - 管有2支疑似汽油彈 #200413葵涌<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>被判入獄</ins></strong><br />\n1. <strong><ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">羅(23) - 判監10個月</span></ins></strong> - 管有伸縮棍、摺刀等 #1117尖沙咀 #理大事件<br />\n<br />\n2. <strong><ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">莊(64) - 判監5星期</span></ins></strong>(保釋等候上訴) - 拍打🐶嚴潔賢胸口及腳踢🐶戚健暉面部 #0922屯門<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>被判入勞教中心<br />\n</ins></strong>1. <strong><ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">蔡(17)</span></ins></strong> - 管有汽油彈、鐵錘 #1111屯門<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>被判入更生中心</ins></strong><br />\n1. <strong><ins><span style=\"color: brown;\">梁(20)</span></ins></strong> - 管有汽油彈 #0907旺角<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">辛苦咁多位手足</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"84adbf48062abe2b1165f82d3696e876a28bdfdd","tid":1979241,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T09:39:19.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\