ard被捕人士關注組only<br />\n請多謝佢哋，及多啲留意下被捕組tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n被捕人士關注組tg channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/s/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fs%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWmhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=27192ad9\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/s/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\nig<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyouarenotalonehk&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWmhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=fd9d35c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/youarenotalonehk</a><br />\n<br />\n法庭文字直播台（去唔到嘅都唔該睇吓直播，關心吓手足）<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWmhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=e742997b\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:39:42.000Z","msg":"copy錯，呢個先啱<br />\n<br />\n法庭文字直播台<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#嚴舜儀署理主任裁判官<br />\n<br />\n👤羅(23) #判刑 🛑已還押149天（#1117尖沙咀 管有違禁武器、管有攻擊性武器:伸縮棍、摺刀、鋸刀、彈叉）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1)管有違禁武器<br />\n（伸縮棍）<br />\n(2)管有攻擊性武器<br />\n（摺刀，鋸刀）<br />\n(3)在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器<br />\n（彈叉及208粒鋼珠）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n案情：<br />\n控方指其2019年11月17日，在科學館道近麼地道交界，管有一支重力操作鋼棒(伸縮警棍)，及一把摺刀、手鋸、彈叉等，並意圖作非法用途。指被告當時帶著黑色背包和另外20多名黑衣人奔跑，被警員截停搜查發現他藏有以上物品，另並有鋼珠、呼吸器、衣物、手套及打火機等。<br />\n<br />\n聽取勞敎報告<br />\n被告醫學上不適合旁教中心<br />\n態度有禮合作，對懲敎官坦誠<br />\n愛運動校隊沒不良記錄<br />\n約束自己行為，還押期間沒犯規條<br />\n後悔衝動，深刻反省，明白承擔法律責任<br />\n重犯機會低。<br />\n<br />\n官判詞：<br />\n-明白被告身體接受唔到一D運動<br />\n-由於控罪嚴重，本住立法精神，必懲罰。<br />\n-考慮去年11月至今扣押多月，索勞敎報告。<br />\n-三控罪，武器性質包括近、中、遠。<br />\n-盡管被告指現場有人給他，但接受同管有乃有意圖目的，一但使用對人有嚴重風險。<br />\n-冇證據有使用，否則控罪更重，考慮被告當時離開中沒使用過<br />\n-伸縮棍9個月起量刑；<br />\n-折刀鋸刀12個月起量刑<br />\n-彈杈同208鋼珠18個月；<br />\n-認罪1/3扣減.<br />\n-即6個月丶8個月丶控罪3額外扣減（考慮年紀同幾個月反省接納真誠改過）當10個月。<br />\n-扣減已還押近五個月可見日子可出獄。<br />\n<br />\n❗️三項罪成<br />\n認罪1/3扣減後分別為<br />\n6個月<br />\n8個月<br />\n10個月<br />\n❗️同期執行即10個月"},{"pid":"457483d950d34178d1693d343384e305dcfcac87","tid":1979241,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73504e32d3680762d1a6f1fda08daac97995659d","tid":1979241,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3bee72a71c69badfcc6d727b9f84d78da3b5804","tid":1979241,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:35:42.000Z","msg":"被判入獄<br />\n1. 羅(23) - 判監10個月 - 管有伸縮棍、摺刀等 #1117尖沙咀 #理大事件<br />\n<br />\n有冇詳情？<br />\n點解咁都入到？<br />\n手足會上訴？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:40:25.000Z","msg":"巴打除咗follow被捕組tg channel外<br />\n都可以follow埋法庭文字直播台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWmhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=e742997b\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live</a>"},{"pid":"2858815aa334633443ab58777d77f2fb7ab5f4e7","tid":1979241,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:41:42.000Z","msg":"手足需要大家，請聽審聲援手足"},{"pid":"8242aca8b7b037d6a90b6560d549e41af9c9bcc8","tid":1979241,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:42:14.000Z","msg":"手足需要大家，請聽審聲援手足"},{"pid":"b40f84478ad46cdf4ccb275dc43744250fd2f506","tid":1979241,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:42:34.000Z","msg":"手足需要大家，請聽審聲援手足"},{"pid":"57e65843e4844733f6779a03cd41b919f8d81247","tid":1979241,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10: